00:22:31,058 --> 00:22:32,350
Sorry for being late.

277
00:22:32,434 --> 00:22:33,727
Happy birthday, Ji-young.

278
00:22:33,810 --> 00:22:35,645
Oh, thanks.

279
00:22:36,229 --> 00:22:37,397
Who…

280
00:22:37,481 --> 00:22:38,648
Oh, hello.

281
00:22:38,732 --> 00:22:40,400
