on the street tonight.

752
00:56:12,160 --> 00:56:13,495
Goodness.

753
00:56:14,287 --> 00:56:15,497
I see.

754
00:56:16,414 --> 00:56:17,999
I'll go.

755
00:56:20,126 --> 00:56:21,795
Work hard, Gyu-rim.

756
00:56:24,589 --> 00:56:26,216
Seriously,

757
00:56:26,299 --> 00:56:28,635
she's so bad at hiding it.

758
00:56:34,808 --> 00:56:36,643
Why did you say that I wasn't here?

759
00:56:38,686 --> 00:56:41,314
I can't tell her
that we were dating at work.

760
00:56:41,397 --> 00:56:43,191
I'll be leaving first.

761
00:56:43,274 --> 00:56:45,026
Come out in five minutes, okay?

762
00:56:45,110 --> 00:56:46,444
What if I get caught?

763
00:56:46,528 --> 00:56:48,905
I'll distract them in the meeting room.

764
00:56:50,532 --> 00:56:52,075
Come out without getting caught.

765
00:56:55,078 --> 00:56:56,037
Okay…

766
00:57:08,133 --> 00:57:11,553
During the last month,
both of you worked very hard

767
00:57:11,636 --> 00:57:13,596
searching for the next CEO at NEXT.

768
00:57:13,680 --> 00:57:15,890
I look forward to seeing what candidates

769
00:57:15,974 --> 00:57:17,392
you will recommend.

